Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fad(0,500)\fs50\fsp8\be25\bord3\shad3\pos(640,555)\c&H82B7D4&\3c&H102D78&\4c&H00195F&\t(\fs35)}剪 辑\N乔·霍贝克
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.64,0:07:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,把白色舰队派往世界各地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fad(0,500)\fs50\fsp8\be25\bord3\shad3\pos(640,555)\c&H82B7D4&\3c&H102D78&\4c&H00195F&\t(\fs35)}艺 术 指 导\N乔纳森·李
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,称其为“善意之旅”
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一样的路数
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.82,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,炫耀武力罢了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.62,0:08:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我得准备一下我的演讲了，谢谢你们，先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fad(0,500)\fs50\fsp8\be25\bord3\shad3\pos(640,555)\c&H82B7D4&\3c&H102D78&\4c&H00195F&\t(\fs35)}摄 影\N杰弗里 C·麦咖特
